snippet.title: Khaos Tracks Beta Gameplay
snippet.description:
Get ready to witness the ultimate rhythm game experience in action! With over 90 pulse-pounding tracks, Khaos Tracks will put your skills to the test. Procedurally generated rhythm notes mean every song is a unique challenge, keeping the gameplay fresh and exciting every time you play.

Choose from four levels of difficulty, from chill beats to pure chaos, and groove to the rhythm while showing off your style with 14 unlockable arrow shaders.

This is rhythm gaming like it's supposed to be —fast, fun, and endlessly replayable. Are you ready to take on the challenge? Let the beat drop and let the chaos begin!
